game.name: Jigsaw Puzzle Big Cities
game.description:
You recently went to Paris and came back with some cute pictures of some major attractions. Out of them, a beautiful sunset and the Eiffel Tower are the most cherishing and lovely frames. Now you have planned to show it to your families and friends. But an accident happened with you and all your photo cards got collapsed and transformed into small pieces. Join Jigsaw Puzzle: Big Cities and get ready to collect a photo that is scattered in multiple pieces

It will be amazing to get all these amazing pictures recovered in this brand new arcade challenge! The screen will show that picture for just a few seconds and then it will be disappeared. Now your job is to drag all the pieces to restore the integrity of the image. There are six unique and challenging levels to play online. Keep completing all the images in the shortest possible time in each level to score big! Do not bother if you get stuck since you can click the eye button to learn about all the elements of your image. 

This cool html5 puzzle game includes more 100 images of multiple streets and cities of Paris. Try to complete each image as fast as you can to hit the screen with some big score! You can enjoy various large beautiful pictures, different challenging puzzles, minimalistic design, and simple interface. This free game would not only help you in improving your mental ability, but it is also worked out as the best choice to warm-up your mind. Have a blast in our other popular titles from the category of puzzle games for kids that you can enjoy without download on atmegame.com!
